rows.label: tlk70000075_05_msg001
rows.name:
Once you set out on your mission,
the Special Inquisitor will make
his move not long after.

rows.label: tlk70000075_05_msg002
rows.name:
Kagutsuchi and Wadatsumi are the
Jewels of the Superbian Empire, so
we cannot let them come to harm.

rows.label: tlk70000075_05_msg004
rows.name:
I am sorry that I am unable to protect
Your Majesty directly at this crucial
time, after all you have done for me.

rows.label: tlk70000075_05_msg005
rows.name:
But both I and the Special Inquisitor
believe from the bottom of our hearts
that you will be successful.

rows.label: tlk70000075_05_msg006
rows.name:
That you will surely return
victorious and bring glory
to the motherland!

rows.label: tlk70000075_05_msg007
rows.name: Fight well, Your Majesty, and be safe!
